#

Crispy Frozen Waffles with Fresh Fruit and Maple Syrup

15 min
$3.5
400 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

QuickBreakfastEasySweet

Description

Crispy frozen waffles topped with sweet fresh fruit and a drizzle of maple syrup for an effortless breakfast.

Ingredients

  • frozen waffles: 2
  • fresh strawberries: 1/2 cup
  • fresh blueberries: 1/2 cup
  • maple syrup: 2 tablespoons
  • butter or non-stick spray (for cooking): 1 teaspoon
